How to Get Coins

Follow the steps below to deposit Stars into your SwarmBet account

1

Join Our Discord Server

If you haven't already, join our community Discord server where all coin transactions are handled by our staff team.

Join Discord
2

Open a Deposit Ticket

Head to the #tickets channel on our Discord and create a new ticket. Select "Deposit" as the ticket type and provide the following info:

  • Your SwarmBet username
  • Amount of Stars you want to deposit
  • Proof of your in-game items / payment
3

Minimum Deposit

There is a minimum deposit requirement to keep transactions fair and manageable for our staff:

3 Star Signs
Minimum per deposit transaction
